.devbootcamp_ticket
  h1 Your Development Bootcamp Ticket

  p Hi #{@student.first_name},

  p First off, thank you for your order. We are excited to welcome you to our Development Bootcamp! Yay!

  p We received your payment and now, as promised, we send you your ticket. We know, it doesn't look like much, but a picture says more than a thousand words right? :)

  p Below is a short recap of the data we received from you. Feel free to ask any questions you might have. You can just reply to this email and we will respond to you shortly.

  table style="border-width: 0; border-style: none;"
    tr
      th style="width: 30%; vertical-align: top; text-align: left;" Name:
      td style="vertical-align: top; text-align: left;" = "#{@student.first_name} #{@student.last_name}"
    tr
      th style="width: 30%; vertical-align: top; text-align: left;" Twitter handle:
      td style="vertical-align: top; text-align: left;" = @student.twitter_handle.present? ? @student.twitter_handle : 'not filled in'
    tr
      th style="width: 30%; vertical-align: top; text-align: left;" Github handle:
      td style="vertical-align: top; text-align: left;" = @student.github_handle.present? ? @student.github_handle : 'not filled in'
    tr
      th style="width: 30%; vertical-align: top; text-align: left;" QR Code:
      td style="vertical-align: top; text-align: left;" = image_tag (root_url + "students/#{@student.identifier}/qr-code.png"), width: 250, height: 250, alt: 'QR Code'

  p
    | You might want to join the buzz at our
    =< link_to 'Facebook event', 'https://www.facebook.com/events/528041797337906/'
    | .

  p
    | See you 12-18 July at
    =< link_to 'Amsterdam Science Park', 'http://www.amsterdamsciencepark.nl/'
    | !

  p Cheers,

  p The Development Bootcamp Team
